 Hyprland

 Focus & Navigate
  SUPER + H/J/K/L          focus left/down/up/right
  SUPER + 1-5, 7           switch workspace
  SUPER + B                toggle browser workspace
  SUPER + D                toggle document workspace
  SUPER + M                toggle media workspace
  SUPER + S                toggle special workspace
  SUPER + G                toggle kondor workspace
  SUPER + Scroll            next/prev workspace

 Move Windows
  SUPER+SHIFT + H/J/K/L    move window left/down/up/right
  SUPER+SHIFT + 1-5, 7     move to workspace
  SUPER+SHIFT + B/D/M/S    move to special workspace

 Window Properties
  SUPER+CTRL + H/L         resize horizontal
  SUPER+CTRL + K/J         resize vertical
  SUPER+CTRL + X           kill window
  SUPER+CTRL + W           toggle floating
  SUPER+CTRL + P           pin window
  SUPER+CTRL + Return      fullscreen
  SUPER+CTRL + T           toggle split
  SUPER + LMB drag         move window
  SUPER + RMB drag         resize window

 Desktop
  SUPER + Q                toggle bar (AGS)
  SUPER + Tab              cycle sidebar
  SUPER + T                toggle periodic table
  SUPER + I                screenshot (snip)
  SUPER+CTRL + I           screenshot (frozen)
  SUPER+SHIFT + I          screenshot monitor
  Print                    screenshot all
  SUPER + P                color picker
  SUPER + R                snap windows

 App Launch
  ALT + Return             foot terminal
  ALT + F                  firefox
  ALT + E                  nemo file manager
  ALT + B                  qutebrowser
  ALT + K                  ttyper
  ALT + Tab                cycle window
  ALT + X                  kill window
  ALT + F4                 kill all windows

 Hardware
  XF86MonBrightness Up/Down  brightness
  XF86PowerOff             suspend & lock
